Naples Daily multimedia journalist J. Scott Butherus and analyst John Weber are at South Fort Myers to get you ready for Week 8 of the high school football season in Southwest Florida. 
Coach Weber talks with Wolfpack head coach Anthony Dixon about taking the reigns as head coach. 
Butherus talks with senior center Ryan Shatzman about the physical test they are going to face in the trenches against Riverdale. Copyright 2015 Journal Media Group. All rights reserved. This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten, or redistributed.
